parameters: Let's check the house.

and the air feels strangely heavy.

the corridor and puts his hand on the door.
Turn the knob as if to kill.

Miko...

when he heard a voice calling \N[5] from outside.

and \N[5]'s legs come to a halt.
But he shook his head and returned to everyone.
